# Wave G-1 fixture plugin files must be committed, including the
# `.mcp.json` sidecar used by the `full-stack` fixture. The repo-root
# `.gitignore` excludes `.mcp.json` globally (to avoid committing
# developer-local MCP configs), so we explicitly un-ignore it here so
# the fixture survives fresh clones.
!full-stack/.mcp.json
